It is proposed that broad responsibilities for monitoring be shared among central agencies and line ministries as follows:
* MFEM monitoring of inputs with line ministries and departments;
* PMO monitoring of outputs with line ministries and departments;

It is proposed that broad responsibilities for monitoring be shared among central agencies and line ministries as follows:
* MFEM monitoring of inputs with line ministries and departments;
* PMO monitoring of outputs with line ministries and departments;
* PMO monitoring of outcomes with line ministries and departments through the ADR, which should include geographical, age and gender disaggregation where possible.
